<h2>🎉 Enrollment Confirmed!</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @family.parents.first&.first_name || 'there' %>,</p>

<p>We're thrilled to officially welcome <strong><%= @child.first_name %></strong> to <%= @program.name %>! Your enrollment is now confirmed and your child's spot for the year is secured.</p>

<h3>Enrollment Summary</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Child:</strong> <%= @child.first_name %> <%= @child.last_name %></li>
  <li><strong>Program:</strong> <%= @program.name %></li>
  <li><strong>Dates:</strong> <%= @program.start_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %>&ndash;<%= @program.end_date.strftime('%b %d, %Y') %></li>
  <% if @program.class_days.present? %>
  <li><strong>Class Days:</strong> <%= @program.class_days %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<% if @payment_plan %>
<h3>Your Payment Plan</h3>
<p>
  <strong><%= @payment_plan.payment_plan.name %></strong><br>
  Total Tuition: $<%= number_with_precision(@payment_plan.total_amount, precision: 2) %><br>
  Enrollment Fee: $<%= number_with_precision(@payment_plan.enrollment_fee, precision: 2) %> (paid)<br>
  <%= @payment_plan.payment_plan.installment_count %> tuition payment(s) of $<%= number_with_precision(@payment_plan.total_amount / @payment_plan.payment_plan.installment_count, precision: 2) %>
</p>
<% end %>

<h3>What's Next?</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Watch for details about your first day and what to bring</li>
  <li>Your tuition installments will follow your selected payment plan</li>
  <li>Reach out any time with questions &mdash; we're here to help</li>
</ol>

<p>We can't wait to explore, play, and learn with <%= @child.first_name %> in nature this year!</p>

<p>Warmly,<br>
The Nature Preschool Team</p>
